									<div class="post_tag"><i class="fa fa-tags"></i><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/akhenaten/" rel="tag">Akhenaten</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/aztecs/" rel="tag">Aztecs</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/bernardino-de-sahagun/" rel="tag">Bernardino de Sahagún</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/codex-ixtlilxochitl/" rel="tag">Codex Ixtlilxóchitl</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/colonialism/" rel="tag">colonialism</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/diego-duran/" rel="tag">Diego Durán</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/diego-munoz-camargo/" rel="tag">Diego Muñoz Camargo</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/fernando-de-alva-ixtlilxochitl/" rel="tag">Fernando de Alva Ixtlilxóchitl</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/hernan-cortes/" rel="tag">Hernan Cortes</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/imperialism/" rel="tag">Imperialism</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/jongsoo-lee/" rel="tag">Jongsoo Lee</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/juan-bautista-pomar/" rel="tag">Juan Bautista Pomar</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/juan-de-torquemada/" rel="tag">Juan de Torquemada</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/king-david/" rel="tag">King David</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/king-solomon/" rel="tag">King Solomon</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/mexican-history/" rel="tag">Mexican history</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/mexico/" rel="tag">Mexico</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/miguel-leon-portilla/" rel="tag">Miguel León-Portilla</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/motecuhzoma-the-elder/" rel="tag">Motecuhzoma the Elder</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/mythology/" rel="tag">mythology</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/myths/" rel="tag">myths</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/nahua/" rel="tag">Nahua</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/nahuatl/" rel="tag">Nahuatl</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/nezahualcoyotl/" rel="tag">Nezahualcóyotl</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/poetry/" rel="tag">poetry</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/restless-books/" rel="tag">Res