ns Rights</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">March 26, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/molly-odintz/">Molly Odintz</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/chris-offutt-on-outlaws-scofflaws-and-kentucky-noir/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/03/reluctant-sheriff-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/chris-offutt-on-outlaws-scofflaws-and-kentucky-noir/">Chris Offutt on Outlaws, Scofflaws, and Kentucky Noir</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">March 26, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/alexdueben/">Alex Dueben</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/tess-gerritsen-summer-guests/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/03/THE-SUMMER-GUESTS-cover-2-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/tess-gerritsen-summer-guests/">The Age of Discontentment: Tess Gerritsen on Senior Crime Solvers and Subverting Expectations</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">March 26, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/johnvaleri/">John B. Valeri</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
